OL,3,CBusiness rates 'double hit' to cost
OL,4,CEnglish firms #2.5 billion next year
OL,6,FBusinesses in England are to face an
OL,7,F"unavoidable double hit" to their
OL,8,Fproperty tax payments next year, which
OL,9,Fwill see total payments surge by about
OL,10,F#2.5 billion, according to new figures.
OL,12,FAnalysis from global tax firm Ryan
OL,13,Findicated that inflation and a
OL,14,Fgovernment tax change will combine to
OL,15,Fdrive up business rates bills further.
