OL,3,CBusiness rates 'double hit' to cost
OL,4,CEnglish firms #2.5 billion next year
OL,6,FBusiness rates are the property taxes
OL,7,Fpaid on commercial properties across
OL,8,Fthe UK and particularly affects high
OL,9,Fstreet businesses. They are devolved
OL,10,Fin Scotland, Wales and Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,FFrom April next year, a nationwide
OL,14,Frevaluation process will take place on
OL,15,Fbusiness rates in England, linking
OL,16,Fpayments to values in the property
OL,17,Fmarket from April 2024.
