OL,3,CBusiness rates 'double hit' to cost
OL,4,CEnglish firms #2.5 billion next year
OL,6,FOn top of this, from April 2026 the
OL,7,FGovernment will introduce a
OL,8,Fsupplementary multiplier of up to 10p
OL,9,Fon properties with a rateable value
OL,10,Fabove #500,000, estimated to affect
OL,11,F17,000 properties nationwide.
OL,13,FThis measure is designed to fund
OL,14,Fpermanently reduced amounts for
OL,15,Fretail, hospitality and leisure
OL,16,Fpremises.
